{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"35337-wheel-s-big-problem","title":"Wheel's Big Problem","description":"Wheel does not like rolling on hot or bumpy roads under Car, so he decides to look for a new vehicle. But Truck is too heavy and he does not fit Bicycle. Then, Wheel meets a boy who is looking for a friend. Can Wheel help the boy? ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Brian Kavanagh"],"illustrators":["Prashant Soni"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/35337-wheel-s-big-problem"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/371263/size3/ee9db84d7d1150b1c86336f3dc04360f.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/371263/size6/ee9db84d7d1150b1c86336f3dc04360f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67998/size6/d5db76762e2ae80a1c1ebc7f0eae2c4b.jpg","text":"Wheel was very upset with Car.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67980/size6/b66f143902433c3cbb41c79b1e56b7c8.jpg","text":"Car often drove Wheel\non very hot roads.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67981/size6/36364d7b3e9bf1a26efe5948e34d6b2c.jpg","text":"Car drove Wheel over sharp stones and through muddy roads.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67982/size6/d86a6ed9d2500f8469a4ad057531c465.jpg","text":"Wheel thought, “Why don't I leave Car?”\nSo, he left to go look for a new vehicle.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67983/size6/b3414d2bd6a31de8981659c8d90ffd15.jpg","text":"Soon, he found Truck.\n“Can I be your wheel?” he asked him.\n\"Sure, of course,\" Truck replied.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67984/size6/cd67d17d2ff17db2ea1f31862005f145.jpg","text":"As Truck drove along, Wheel screamed,\n“Oh no, you are too heavy,\nI will get crushed!”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67985/size6/464f4bf8ef8e2f62ecdac416564668c6.jpg","text":"Wheel left Truck\n in \nsearch of another vehicle.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67986/size6/1c4572d851a35a6860a4283408818994.jpg","text":"Next, he found Tuk Tuk. \n“Can I be your wheel?”\nhe asked.\n“Yes, of course!” Tuk Tuk\nreplied.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67987/size6/d4028ada044dfac81116f2cea02f5122.jpg","text":"As Tuk Tuk drove, he screamed, “Get off or you will overturn me!“\nWheel left to find another vehicle.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67988/size6/2876fe89195df7d44ea8ba39fcef8b07.jpg","text":"Wheel asked Bicycle if he could join him.\n“No, you are not the same size,” replied Bicycle.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67989/size6/734e00928fe8d845c07d0b27227b8f64.jpg","text":"Next, Wheel asked Horse-Cart. \nBut that didn't work out either.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67990/size6/bcf6c867f315b93a56b8df7418841755.jpg","text":"Tired and sad, Wheel sat under a tree.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67991/size6/c3c370884071327d7f928c59cfb7f1a9.jpg","text":"A boy came by and asked him, “Will you be my friend?”\n“Yes!” Wheel said.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67992/size6/cb5db6dd87a9ba6bfa630bd86b5e3332.jpg","text":"Now they swing together.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67993/size6/986ce144289e175157651c50206a0649.jpg","text":"They play together.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/67997/size6/af67b76ea2ebc2f89bd0d22aadf8c657.jpg","text":"They do everything together.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":180}}